<div class="section-container">
  <section class="section secondary">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="has-text-centered section-title">Solution overview</h2>
      <div class="columns is-centered has-margin-top-40 inverted-mobile">
          <div class="column is-half">
          <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Automated permit check</h3>
          <p class="muted">By implementing LTO Network into the system to issue and verify the permits, the transportation request can be approved automatically. The data is directly shared with the waste processor and authorities in case of a cross-border transportation.  </p>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-container solutions column is-centered" style="left:48px;width:280px;height:250px;background-image: url('https://via.placeholder.com/150x150?text=LivIcon')">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="columns is-centered has-margin-top-40">
            <div class="icon-container solutions column is-centered" style="left:48px;width:280px;height:250px;background-image: url('https://via.placeholder.com/150x150?text=LivIcon')">
            </div>
          <div class="column is-half">
        <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Data re-use</h3>
          <p class="muted">The transportation companies can use their smartphones to show their transportation documentation to the authorities in case of a random check. The inspectorate is able to derive the data directly from the blockchain of LTO Network.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="columns is-centered has-margin-top-40 inverted-mobile">
        <div class="column is-half">
          <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Connecting systems</h3>
          <p class="muted">By digitizing the protocol that already existed on paper into a 'Live Contract' parties where able to connect their existing systems to LTO Network to communicate, share data and notifications real time. </p>
        </div>
          <div class="icon-container solutions column is-centered" style="left:48px;width:280px;height:250px;background-image: url('https://via.placeholder.com/150x150?text=LivIcon')">
        </div>
