    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="has-text-centered section-title">Advantages using LTO Network</h2>
      <div class="columns is-centered has-margin-top-40">
        <div class="icon-container advantages column is-one-quarter" style="left:48px;height:250px;background-image: url('/assets/rocks/rock-1.svg')">
          <img style="position:absolute;width:26px;top:90px;left:-40px" src="/assets/small-rock-2.svg">
          <img style="position:absolute;width:70px;top:20px;left:-20px" src="/assets/small-rock-1.svg">
        </div>
        <div class="column is-two-thirds">
          <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Reduction of manual process handling</h3>
          <p class="muted">Administrative tasks such as manual entering data into your system that receive by letter, fax or email belongs to the past. With the blockchain technology of LTO Network all parties now receive structured data. They now benefit from data re-us and automated status updates which reduces manual handling with more then 30%. </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="columns is-centered has-margin-top-40">
        <div class="icon-container advantages column is-one-quarter" style="left:48px;height:250px;background-image: url('/assets/rocks/rock-1.svg')">
          <img style="position:absolute;width:26px;top:90px;left:-40px" src="/assets/small-rock-2.svg">
          <img style="position:absolute;width:70px;top:20px;left:-20px" src="/assets/small-rock-1.svg">
        </div>
        <div class="column is-two-thirds">
          <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Cost savings</h3>
          <p class="muted">Parties that collaboration using LTo Network are able to keep using their own system to participate in the process while benefiting from data re-used, automated checks and verification and real time status updates. By enabling LTO Network you can realize up to 50% reduction on administrative overhead.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="columns is-centered has-margin-top-40">
        <div class="icon-container advantages column is-one-quarter" style="left:48px;height:250px;background-image: url('/assets/rocks/rock-1.svg')">
          <img style="position:absolute;width:26px;top:90px;left:-40px" src="/assets/small-rock-2.svg">
          <img style="position:absolute;width:70px;top:20px;left:-20px" src="/assets/small-rock-1.svg">
        </div>
        <div class="column is-two-thirds">
          <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Build-in compliance with the privacy- and GDPR laws</h3>
          <p class="muted">GDPR regulation makes it difficult to use new technology such as blockchain. With LTO Network we have built in privacy by design. Every party involved 'signs' a transaction, whether that's a step in a workflow or upload of a new document. A 'live Contract' can b structured in such way that it can delete the data atomically after a certain step has been executed, or if the process is older then for instance 24 months.   </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    <div class="columns is-centered has-margin-top-40">
        <div class="column">
<table class="table advantages">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th class="table-icon"></td>
          <th class="dark-indigo" colspan="2">Theme</th>
          <th class="dark-indigo" colspan="2">LTO Network solution</th>
          <th class="dark-indigo" colspan="2">Traditional solution</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>

      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <th class="table-icon"></td>
          <th class="deep-lavender">Automation</th>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-checkmark" src="/assets/table icon - good.svg"> </td>
          <td class="steel">Using LTO Network to collaborate on multi-stakeholder processes benefits from data re-use, real time status updates and notifications. </td>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-x" src="/assets/table icon - bad.svg"></td>
          <td class="steel">Collaboration on a processes that runs between multiple parties is hard to automate as communication happens via email, phone and letters which produces unstructured data.</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
          <th class="table-icon"></td>
          <th class="deep-lavender">Data sharing</th>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-checkmark" src="/assets/table icon - good.svg"> </td>
          <td class="steel">Using blockchain technology of LTO Network organizations can share the data in a GDPR complaint and the data can be trusted as it is immutable and signed by the party that submitted the data. </td>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-x" src="/assets/table icon - bad.svg"></td>
          <td class="steel">Relying on the system that is managed by your counter-party does not provide a level playing field. Parties don’t want to share more data than strictly required to complete the process.</td>
        </tr>


        <tr>
          <th class="table-icon"></td>
          <th class="deep-lavender">Existing systems</th>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-checkmark" src="/assets/table icon - good.svg"> </td>
          <td class="steel">By simply connecting API’s of you existing applications to th LTO Network Node, you and every other stakeholder involved is able to participate on the workflow while keeping existing IT in place.</td>
          <td class="table-icon"> <img class="table-x" src="/assets/table icon - bad.svg"></td>
          <td class="steel">‘Traditional’ blockchain solutions require large and costly IT overhauls due to existing (legacy) systems.</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
        </tr>
      </tbody>

    </table>
